    "en": {
      "title": "Electricity will be cut for three hours today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Janaka Rathnayake, Chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, said that due to lack of fuel for electricity generation, the 3-hour power cut was allowed to be implemented again today.",
        "Accordingly, Mr. Janaka Ratnayake further stated that electricity will be cut for 20 zones from 'A' to 'W' for 1 hour and 40 minutes during the day and 1 hour and 20 minutes at night."
      ],
